description:
Are you ready for some changes in your life that will benefit you for eterinity? If so, "26 Self Improvement Thoughts" is the ebook for you!

In this book are 26 thoughts to better your life concerning the areas of attraction and self development. Be prepared to meet new people and find new opportunities as you become better at what you do and how you think.
